hadiths[52]{hadithnumber,text}:
1198,"Ummul-momenin Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke (shuroo mein) safar aur hazar ki Namaz do-do rakatein hi farz hui thi , phir safar ki Namaz bahaal rakhi gaee aur muqeem ki Namaz mein izafa kar diya gaya."
1199,Janab Y'alaa bin Umayya kehtey hain maine Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : bataaiye ke logon ka (safar mein) Namaz qasr karna kyon kar hai? halanke Shan wale Allah ne farmaya hai : ''agar tumhen dar mehsoos ho ke kuffar tumhen fitney mein dal dengey . ... ''aur ab kuffar se dar khof wali kaifiyat to khatam ho chuki hai. unhoney jawab diya ke mujhey bhi yehi tajjub hua tha jo tumhen hua hai. isliye maine ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz ki thi. aapney farmaya tha : ''ye sadqa hai jo Allah taala ne tum par kiya hai. so uska sadqa qubul karo.''
1200,"Janab ibne-Juraij kehtey hain ke maine Abdullah bin Ubai Ammar ko suna, wo bayan kartey they. aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Abu-Aasim aur Hammad bin Musada ne bhi ibne Bakr ki manind riwayat kiya hai."
1201,"Yahya bin Yazid Hunaee kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se Namaz-qasr kerney ke baarey mein sawal kiya, to unhoney farmaya : ''Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab teen meel ya teen farsakh ki masafat par jatey to do rakatein padha kartey they.'' ye shak Shoba ko hua hai."
1202,Hazrat Anas kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Madiney mein Zohar ki Namaz chaar rakaat padhi aur Asr ki Namaz Zul-Hulaifa mein do rakaat.
1203,Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna aap farmatey they : '' tumhara rab bakriyon ke us charwahey par tajjub karta (khush hota) hai jo pahad ki choti par (akela hotey huey) Namaz ke liye Azan kehta aur Namaz padhta hai. Shan wala Allah farmata hai : dekho merey us bandey ko jo Namaz ke liye Azan aur iqaamat kehta hai (aur) mujhi se darta hai. maine apney us bandey ko bakhsh diya hai aur jannat mein dakhil kar diya hai.''
1204,"Mishaaj bin Musa kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se jo suna hai bayan kijiye ! to unhoney kaha : ham jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath safar mein hua kartey to aap Zohar ki Namaz padhtey , phir koochh kartey halanke hamein shubha sa hota tha ke Suraj dhalaa bhi hai ya nahin."
1205,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi manzil par padaaw kartey to us waqt tak koochh na kartey jab tak ke Zohar ki Namaz na padh letey. eik shakhs ne un se kaha : agar-che nisfun-nahaar hi hota? unhoney kaha ke) haan ! ( agar-che nisfun-nahaar hi hota ."
1206,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke wo log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ghazwae-tabuk ke liye nikley to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zohar aur Asr aur maghrib aur Isha ki namazon ko jama kiya kartey they. aapney eik din Namaz ko muakhkhar kar diya (late kar diya) , phir tashrif laye aur Zohar aur Asr ikhatti padhaeen , phir apney khemey mein chaley gaey, phir tashrif laye aur maghrib aur Isha ikhatti padhaeen."
1207,"Janab Naafe se riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko Makka mein unki ehliya Hazrat Safiya ki baabat pukara gaya. (yani unki wafat ki khabar di gaee) to aapney safar kiya, yahan tak ke Suraj ghuroob ho gaya aur sitarey nikal aaye aur kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab safar mein jaldi mein hotey to un dono namazon (yani maghrib aur Isha) ko jama kar liya kartey they, chunanche aap chaltey rahey, yahan tak ke shafaq ghayeb ho gaee , tab utrey aur dono namazon ko jama karkey padha."
1208,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul (naqal ki gaee) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghazwae-tabuk mein agar kooch kerney se pehley Suraj dhal jata to Zohar aur Asr ko jama kar letey aur agar Suraj dhalney se pehley hi kooch kartey to Zohar ko muakhkhar kar letey , yahan tak ke Asr ke waqt utartey (aur unhen jama karkey padhtey.) aur maghrib mein bhi aisey hi kartey yani agar safar shuru kerney se pehley Suraj ghuroob ho jata to maghrib aur Isha ko jama kar letey. aur agar Suraj ghuroob honey se pehley hi chal padtey to maghrib ko muakhkhar kar letey , yahan tak ke Isha ke liye utartey aur in dono ko ikhattey padhtey. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke is hadees ko Hisham bin Urwa ne Husain bin Abdullah sey, unhoney kuraib sey, unhoney ibne-Abbas sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se hadees mufazzal aur Leis ki manind bayan ki hai."
1209,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne namaze-Maghrib aur Isha ko safar mein sirf eik hi baar jama farmaya tha. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke ye riwayat ba-waasta Ayub , Naafe se aur wo Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se mauqufan bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko sirf usi raat dekha gaya tha ke unhoney maghrib aur Isha ko jama karkey padha tha, yani jis raat unhen unki ehliya Hazrat Safiya ki tashweeshnaak khabar pahunchi thi. jabkey Mak'hool se Naafe ki sanad se ye marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne eik ya do baar aisey kiya tha."
1210,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zohar aur Asr aur maghrib aur Isha ki namaazen baghair kisi khauf ya safar ke ikhatti padheen. Imam Malik kehtey hain : mera khayal hai ke barish mein aisey kiya tha. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Hammad bin Salma ne Abu-Zubair se isi ki manind riwayat kiya hai jabkey Qurra bin Khalid ne Abu-Zubair se riwayat kiya to kaha : wo safar jo ham ne tabuk ki janib kiya tha (us mein aapney ye namaazen jama karkey padhi thin).
1211,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Madina mein (muqeem hotey huey) baghair kisi khauf ya barish ke Zohar aur Asr ki aur maghrib aur Isha ki namaazen jama karkey padhein . Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchha gaya ke aap ka us se kya maqsad tha? unhoney kaha : yehi ke ummat ko mashaqqat na ho.
1212,"Janab Naafe aur Abdullah bin Waaqid se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke muazzan ne Namaz ke liye kaha, to unhoney kaha : chalo chalo , yahan tak ke shafaq ghuroob honey se zara pehley utrey aur maghrib ki Namaz padhi , phir intizar kiya, yahan tak ke shafaq ghayeb ho gaee to Isha padhi , phir farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab kisi kaam mein jaldi hoti to aisey hi kartey they jaisey ke maine kiya hai. phir aapney us din raat mein teen din ki masafat tey ki . Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : ibne-Jabir ne Naafe se apni sanad se usi ki manind riwayat kiya."
1213,Esa ne ibne Jabir se isi ke ham-maani riwayat kiya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Abdullah bin Ala ne Naafe se riwayat kartey huey kaha hai : jab shafaq ghuroob honey lagi to wo ( ibne-Umar ( utrey aur namaazen jama karkey padhin.
1214,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Madiney mein ham ko aath rakatein aur saat rakatein yani Zohar w Asr aur maghrib w Isha ki namaazen (jama karkey) padhaeen. Sulaiman aur Musaddad ne ye nahin kaha ke ''hamein padhaeen'' (balke ye kaha ke aapney padhin). Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Saleh Maula Tawama ki riwayat mein jo ibne-Abbas se hai, kaha : ''baghair barish ke.'' (ye namaazen jama kin.)"
1215,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Suraj Makka mein ghuroob ho gaya. phir aapney ( maghrib aur Isha ki namaazen) wadi sarf mein ja kar jama karkey padhin.
1216,Hisham bin Saad bayan kartey hain ke Makka aur wadi sarf ke darmiyan das meel ka fasla hai.
1217,"Janab Abdullah bin Dinar kahtey hain ke Suraj ghuroob ho gaya jabkey main Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke paas tha. ham chaltey rahey, jab ham ne dekha ke khoob shaam ho gaee hai to ham ne arz kiya : Namaz ? magar wo chaltey rahey, yahan tak ke shafaq ghayeb ho gaee aur sitarey nikal aaye to wo utrey aur dono namaazen ikhatti karkey padhin. phir kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ko jab safar mein jaldi hoti to namaazen meri usi Namaz ki tarah padhtey they. yani andhera chha janey ke baad dono ko jama karkey padhtey they. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke isko Aasim bin Muhammad ne apney bhai sey, unhoney Salim se riwayat kiya hai. aur ibne-Abi Najeeh ne Ismail bin Abdur-Rehman bin Zuaib se riwayat kiya hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka un namazon ko jama karna ghuroob shafaq ke baad tha."
1218,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Suraj dhalney se pehley kooch kartey , to Zohar ko Asr ke waqt tak muakhkhar kar letey. phir utartey aur un dono ko jama karkey padhtey . aur agar safar shuru kerney se pehley hi Suraj dhal jata to Zohar padhtey aur Sawar ho jatey. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Mufazzal (mazkura hadees ke eik raawi ( Misr ke qazi they. Mujaab ul daawaah الدعوۃ they aur wo Fazaala ke sahibzadey hain."
1219,"Janab Aqeel ne apni sanad se ye hadees bayan ki, unhoney kaha : aur maghrib ko muakhkhar kar letey aur Isha ke sath jama karkey padhtey , jabkey shafaq ghuroob ho chuki hoti."
1220,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghazwae-tabuk mein jab Suraj dhalney se pehley kooch kartey to Zohar ko muakhkhar kartey , yahan tak ke Asr ke sath jama karkey padhtey . aur jab Suraj dhalney ke baad kooch kartey , to Zohar aur Asr ko ikhatta padhtey, phir safar shuru kartey. aur jab maghrib se pehley rawana hotey to maghrib ko muakhkhar kartey , yahan tak ke Isha ke sath mila ke padhtey . aur jab maghrib ke baad kooch kartey , to Isha ko jaldi karkey maghrib ke sath padh letey. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke is hadees ko sirf Quteba ne riwayat kiya hai. (yani Leis se riwayat kerney mein munfarid hain.)"
1221,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eik safar mein nikley , aapney hamein Isha ki Namaz padhaai to aapney uski eik rakat mein sura ( والتين والزيتون ( tilawat farmaai."
1222,Hazrat Bara bin Aazib Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main atthaara safaron mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath raha hun. maine nahin dekha ke aapney Suraj dhal janey ke baad Zohar se pehley do rakatein chhodi hon.
1223,"Janab Hafs bin Aasim bin umr bin Khattab ka bayan hai ke main eik safar mein Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath tha, unhoney ham ko do rakatein padhaeen , phir (apni manzil mein) aagey aur kuch logon ko qiyam kartey dekha aur puchha ke ye log kya kar rahey hain? maine kaha : ye nafl padh rahey hain. unhoney kaha : agar mujhey nafl hi padhney hotey to main apni (farz) Namaz puri kar leta . aey bhatijey ! main safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath raha hun, aapney do rakaaton se ziyada nahin padhin, yahan tak ke Allah ne unko qabz kar liya. aur main Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki sohbat mein raha hun, unhoney bhi do rakaat se ziyada nahin padhin, yahan tak ke Allah taala ne unko qabz kar liya . aur main Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki sohbat mein raha hun, unhoney bhi do rakaat se ziyada nahin padhein , yahan tak ke Allah ne unko qabz kar liya . aur main Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki sohbat mein raha hun, unhoney bhi do rakaat se ziyada nahin padhein , yahan tak ke Shan Wale Allah ne unko qabz kar liya aur Allah taala ka farman hai : ''tumharey liye Allah ke Rasool mein behtareen namoona hai.''"
1224,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni sawari par nafl aur witr padha kartey they, uska rukh chahey kisi taraf hi hota magar aap farz Namaz us par na padhtey they."
1225,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul (naqal ki gaee) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab safar mein hotey aur nafl padhna chahtey to apni oontni ko qibla rukh kartey aur takbire-tahreema keh kar Namaz shuru kar letey , phir Namaz padhtey rehtey , chahey uska rukh kisi bhi taraf hota rehta."
1226,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap apney gadhey par Namaz padh rahey they aur aap ka munh khaibar ki taraf tha.
1227,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey kisi kaam ke liye bheja . main wapis aaya to dekha ke aap apni oontni par Namaz padh rahey they, aap ka rukh mashriq ki taraf tha aur aap sajdey ke liye rukoo se ziyada jhuktey they."
1228,"Janab Ata bin Abi Ribah ne Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kiya ke kya aurton ko ijazat hai ke apni sawari ke janweron par Namaz padh liya keren? unhoney jawab diya ke kisi haal mein unhen iski ijazat nahin di gaee hai, pareshani ki kaifiyat ho ya itminan ki . Muhammad bin Shuaib ne kaha : ye faraaiz ki baat hai."
1229,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke saath (60) ghazwey kiye hain aur Fateh Makka mein bhi aap ke sath tha. aap Makka mein atthaara raaten thehrey. un dino mein aap do do rakatein hi padhtey rahey aur farmatey : ''aey ehale-shehar ! tum chaar rakatein padho , ham log musafir hain.''"
1230,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka mein sattarah din thehrey aur Namaz qasr kartey rahey . Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : jo shakhs sattarah din iqaamat karey wo qasr karey aur jo us se ziyada thehrey wo puri Namaz padhey. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Ibad bin Mansoor ne Ikrima se unhoney ibne-Abbas se riwayat kartey huey kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Unais din qiyam kiya.
1231,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Fateh Makka ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) makkey mein pandarah din rahey aur qasr kartey rahey. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke is hadees ko Abdah bin Sulaiman , Ahmed bin Khalid Wahbi aur Salma bin Fazal ne ibne Is'haq se riwayat kiya hai. ye log Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka zikr nahin kartey."
1232,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka mein sattarah din thehrey aur do do rakatein padhtey rahey.
1233,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Madina se Makka ki taraf rawana huey. aap (is safar mein) do do rakatein hi padhtey rahey, yahan tak ke ham Madina lot aaye . ham ne puchha : kya aap log wahan kuch thehrey bhi they? unhoney kaha : das din thehrey they."
1234,"Janab umr bin Ali bin Abi Talib se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) jab safar kartey to Suraj ghuroob honey ke baad chaltey , yahan tak ke andhera chha janey ke qarib ho jata. phir (sawari sey) utartey aur maghrib ki Namaz padhtey, khana talab karkey ishaaiya kartey , phir Isha ki Namaz padhtey , phir kooch kartey , aur bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisey hi kiya kartey they. Usman (bin abi Sheba) ne Abdullah bin Muhammad bin umr bin Ali se (an) ke saath riwayat kiya hai (jabkey ibne Musanna ne (akhbirni (mujhe khabar mili hai)) kaha hai.) (Abu-Ali kehtey hain ke) maine Imam Abu-Dawud ko suna, wo kehtey they ke Usama bin Zaid ne Hafs bin Ubaidullah yani ibne  Anas bin Malik se naqal kiya ke Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) maghrib aur Isha ki namaazen jama kartey aur ghuroob shafaq ke baad padhtey they aur kehtey they : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisey hi kiya kartey they. Zohri ki riwayat Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) isi ke misl (jaisi) hai."
1235,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tabuk mein bees din thehrey aur Namaz qasr kartey rahey. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke sirf Maamer hi ne isey musnad bayan kiya hai. (doosrey mursal bayan kartey hain.)
1236,"Hazrat Abu Aaysha Zarqi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath asfaan mein they jabkey mushrekin ki qiyaadat Khalid bin Waleed ke haath mein thi. ham ne Zohar ki Namaz padhi. mushrekin ne kaha : hamein dhokey ka mauqa mila tha, hamein ghaflat ka mauqa mila tha agar ham in par hamla kar detey jabkey ye Namaz padh rahey they ( to ye bahut achchhaa mauqa tha ( chunanche Zohar aur Asr ke darmiyan aayat qasr (yani Namaze-khauf ( nazil ho gaee . jab Asr ka waqt hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qibley ki janib khadey ho gaey aur mushrekin unke samney they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey eik saf khadi hui aur dusri uskey peechhey. so Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rukoo kiya aur sab logon ne bhi rukoo kiya. phir aapney sajda kiya aur aap ke muttasil (se lagi hui) jo saf thi usney sajda kiya. dusri saf waley khadey unki nigrani kartey rahey. jab un logon ( pehli saf walon ( ne do sajdey kar liye aur khadey ho gaey to jo log unke peechhey they unhoney sajda kiya. phir pehli saf dusri saf walon ki jagah par aa gaee aur dusri saf waley pehli saf walon ki jagah par ho gaey. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur sab logon ne rukoo kiya. phir aapney aur aap se muttasil saf walon ne sajda kiya aur pichhli saf waley khadey unki nigrani kartey rahey. phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur pehli saf waley baith gaey to doosron ne sajda kiya. phir sab baithey aur ikhattey salam phera. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Asfaan aur ghazwa bani Sulaim ke mauqe par is tarah Namaz (khauf) padhaai. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Ayub aur Hisham ne Abu-Zubair sey, unhoney Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se isi ke ham-maani riwayat bayan ki hai. aisey hi Dawud bin Husain ne Ikrima sey, unhoney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kiya hai. aur aisey hi Abdul-Malik ne Ata sey, unhoney Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. isi tarah Qatada ne Hasan sey, unhoney Hittaan sey, unhoney Abu-Musa se unka apna kaam naqal kiya hai. aur isi tarah Ikrima bin Khalid ne Mujahid sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se. aur Hisham bin Urwa ne apney walid sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya hai. aur Sauri ka bhi yehi qaul hai."
1237,"Hazrat Sehal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney as-haab ko Namaze-khauf padhaai. aapney apney peechhey un logon ki do safen banaeen. to jo log aap ke sath khadey they aapney unhen eik rakat padhaai. phir aap khadey ho gaey aur musalsal khadey rahey, yahan tak ke unhon (pehli saf walon) ne apni dusri rakaat padh li . phir doosrey giroh waley aagey aagey aur jo aagey they wo peechhey chaley gaey. isliye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un logon ko bhi eik rakat padhaai phir baithey rahey, yahan tak ke unhon (doosrey giroh walon) ne apni dusri rakaat padh li , phir salam phera ."
1238,"Saleh bin Khawaat us shakhs se riwayat kartey hain jisney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ghazwae zatur-riqaa mein Namaze khauf padhi thi, usney bayan kiya ke eik giroh ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath saf banai aur doosra giroh dushman ke samney raha . phir aapney us giroh ko jo aap ke sath tha eik rakat padhaai , phir khadey rahey aur unhoney apni dusri rakaat mukammal ki . phir ye log dushman ke samney chaley gaey aur doosra giroh aa gaya. aapney unko apni baqi maanda (bachi hui) dusri rakaat padhaai, phir aap baithey rahey aur un logon ne apney taur par apni Namaz mukammal ki. phir aapney unke sath salam phera. Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke) Namaze-khauf ke silsiley mein) jo maine suna hai (un mein se yehi) hadees Yazid bin Roomaan mujhey ziyada pasand hai."
1239,"Saleh bin khawaat Ansari se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Sehal bin Abi Hasma Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se bayan kiya ke Namaze-khauf (ka tariqa) ye hai ke Imam aur uskey sathiyon ka eik giroh ( Namaz ke liye ( khadey ho jaeyn aur doosra giroh dushman ke muqabley mein khada rahey. Imam apney sath walon ke sath rukoo karey aur sajda karey, phir jab uthey to khada hi rahey aur muqtadi apney taur par dusri rakaat padhein, phir salam pheren aur Imam khada rahey aur ye dushman ke muqabil chaley jaeyn . phir doosra giroh aa jaey jinhon ne abhi Namaz shuru nahin ki thi , isliye wo Imam ke peechhey takbir keh kar) Namaz shuru keren ( phir Imam unko rukoo aur sajda kiraaey , phir salam pherey aur ye log khadey ho kar apni baqiya rakaat padhen aur phir salam pheren. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Yahya bin Saeed ki Qasim se riwayat Yazid bin Roomaan ki riwayat ki manind hai sirf salam ke baarey mein ikhtilaf kiya hai. aur Ubaidullah ki riwayat Yahya bin Saeed ki riwayat ki manind hai. us ( Yahya (ke lafz hain ( ويثبت قائما ( (yani Imam khada rahey)."
1240,"Marwan bin Hakam se riwayat hai ke usney Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha , kya aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein Namaze-khauf padhi hai? Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : haan ! Marwan ne puchha Kab ? unhoney kaha : ghazwae-najad ke saal. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Asr ki Namaz ke liye khadey huey aur aap ke sath eik giroh tha jabkey doosra dushman ke muqabil tha aur qibley ki taraf unki pusht thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne takbir (tahreema) kahi aur sab ne aap ke sath takbir kahi , aap ke sath walon ne bhi aur unhoney bhi jo dushman ke bilmuqaabil they. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney sath waley giroh ko eik rakat padhaai. us giroh ne aap ke sath rukoo kiya, phir aapney sajda kiya to unhoney bhi sajda kiya. jabke doosrey log dushman ke samney khadey rahey. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huey aur aap ke sath wala giroh bhi khada ho gaya. phir ye chaley gaey aur dushman ke samney ja khadey huey aur doosra giroh jo pehley dushman ke samney tha (aap ke peechhey) aa gaya. unhoney (apney taur par) rukoo aur sajda kiya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) badastoor khadey rahey. phir (jab ye log pehli rakaat sey) khadey huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko dusri rakaat padhaai. unhoney aap ke sath rukoo aur sajda kiya. phir wo giroh bhi aa gaya jo dushman ke samney tha, unhoney (apney taur par) rukoo aur sajda kiya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke sath waley baithey rahey. phir salam phera, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aur sab ne ikatthey salam phera. isliye (is tarah) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki) jamaat ke sath ( do rakatein huin aur dono girohon mein se har har shakhs ki eik-eik rakat."
1241,"Janab Urwa bin Zuber Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unka bayan hai ke ham log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Najad ki janib nikley. yahan tak ke jab ham maqame-nakhl ke zatur-riqaa mein pahunchey to banu-ghatfaan ki eik jamaat se mudbhed ho gaee . aur mazkura riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kiya. iskey alfaz Hewa ke alfaz se mukhtalif hain. is mein kaha : jab aapney apney sath walon ke sath rukoo aur sajda kiya aur khadey huey to ye log ultey paon chaltey huey apney sathiyon ki jagah ja khadey huey . aur qibley ki taraf pusht kerney ka zikr nahin kiya."
1242,"Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Ubaidullah bin Saad ne ham se bayan kiya to kaha ke mujh se merey chacha ne bayan kiya, unhoney kaha ke merey walid ne mujhey khabar di ibne Is'haq sey, unhoney kaha ke mujh se Muhammad bin Jaafar bin Zuber ne bayan kiya hai ke Urwa bin Zuber ne un se bayan kiya ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne un se yehi waqia bayan kiya. kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne takbir kahi aur us giroh ne bhi takbir kahi jisney aap ke sath saf banai thi. phir aapney rukoo kiya to unhoney bhi rukoo kiya. phir aapney sajda kiya to unhoney bhi sajda kiya, phir aapney sar uthaya to unhoney bhi uthaya . phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baithey rahey aur un logon ne apney taur par doosra sajda kiya. phir wo khadey huey aur ultey paon chaltey huey un (yani doosrey giroh) ke peechhey ja khadey huey aur doosra giroh aa gaya, wo khadey huey aur unhoney takbir kahi aur apney taur par rukoo kiya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sajda kiya to unhoney aap ke sath sajda kiya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho gaey aur un logon ne apney taur par doosra sajda kiya. phir dono giroh ikhattey khadey huey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi. aapney rukoo kiya to unhoney rukoo kiya, phir aapney sajda kiya to sab ne sajda kiya. phir palat kar doosra sajda kiya, unhoney bhi aap ke sath jaldi se sajda kiya, nihayat jaldi , jald bazi mein koi kasar na chhodi . phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne salam phera , to un sab ne bhi salam phera . phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho gaey, aur sab log aap ke sath sari Namaz mein shareek rahey ."
1243,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik giroh ko eik rakat padhaai jabke doosra giroh dushman ke samney tha. phir ye log chaley gaey aur doosron ki jagah par) dushman ke muqabil ( khadey ho gaey . phir wo log ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey ( aagey to aapney unko dusri rakaat padhaai aur salam pher diya. phir ye log khadey huey aur apni rakaat ada ki aur doosrey giroh waley bhi khadey huey aur apni rakaat ada ki . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Naafe aur Khalid bin Maadaan ne ibne-Umar sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aisey hi riwayat kiya hai. Masruq aur Yusuf bin Mehraan ka bhi ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se yehi qaul hai. neez (isi ke sath) Yunus ne Hasan sey, unhoney Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se unka kaam bayan kiya hai."
1244,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein Namaze-khauf padhaai. (mujahideen ne do safein banaeen) eik saf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey khadi hui aur dusri dushman ke samney rahi. aapney unko (jo aap ke peechhey they) eik rakat padhaai, phir doosrey aagey aur un logon ki jagah par khadey ho gaey aur ye dushman ke muqabley mein chaley gaey . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko eik rakat padhaai aur khud salam pher diya, to un logon ne uth kar apni eik rakat padhi aur salam phera , phir chaley gaey aur un logon ki jagah par ja khadey huey . jo dushman ke samney they. phir doosrey un logon ki jagah par aagey aur apni-apni eik rakat padhi aur salam phera."
1245,"Janab Khusaif ne apni sanad se uskey ham-maani bayan kiya. is riwayat mein hai : Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne takbir kahi to dono safon ne unke sath mil kar takbir kahi . Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Sauri ne bhi Khusaif se usi ke ham-maani riwayat kiya hai. aur Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi aisey hi padhaai thi , siwaye uskey ke jis giroh ne akheer mein unke sath eik rakat padhi , wo Imam ke salam ke baad dushman ke samney chaley gaey . phir pehla giroh aaya aur usney apney taur par eik rakat padhi (jo baqi thi) phir ye doosrey giroh ki jagah par laut gaey, iske baad doosra giroh aaya aur usney eik rakat padhi . Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : hamein ye Muslim bin Ibrahim ne bayan kiya ke hamein Abdus-Samad bin Habib ne bayan kiya, wo apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke un logon ne Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath kaabul mein jihad kiya aur unhoney ham ko Namaze-khauf padhaai."
1246,"Janab Saulab bin Zahdam bayan kartey hain ke ham log Hazrat Saeed bin al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tabristaan mein they, wo khadey huey aur puchha : tum mein se kaun hai jisney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaze-khauf padhi hai? Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main hun. chunanche unhoney eik giroh ko eik rakat padhaai aur doosrey ko eik , aur phir un logon ne koi adaegi nahin ki (doosri rakaat ada na ki). Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Ubaidullah bin Abdullah aur Mujahid ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aisey hi riwayat kiya hai. aur Abdullah bin Shaqiq ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aur Yazid al Faqeer aur Abu-Musa , ye eik Taabai hain ( Sahibe-Rasool Abu-Musa ( Ash'ari nahin hain. ye sab Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se. baaz ne Shoba se Yazid al Faqeer ki riwayat mein kaha hai : unhoney eik rakat ada ki thi. aur aisey hi isko Samaak Hanfi ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya hai. aur aisey hi isko Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya hai. is soorat mein qaum ke liye eik eik rakat hui aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye do rakatein."
1247,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke Shan wale Allah ne tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zaban par Namaz farz ki hai. iqaamat mein chaar rakatein , safar mein do rakatein aur khauf main eik rakat ."
1248,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khauf mein Zohar ki Namaz padhaai . baaz ne aap ke peechhey saf banai aur baaz dushman ke samney rahey . aapney un logon ko) jo aap ke peechhey they ( do rakatein padhaeen aur salam pher diya. tab ye log apney sathiyon ki jagah chaley gaey aur wo aagey aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padhi . aapney unko do rakatein padhaeen aur salam phera . is tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki chaar rakatein huin aur aap ke as-haab ki do do. Janab Hasan isi ka fatwa diya kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain aur aisey hi namaze-Maghrib mein (hoga ke) Imam ki chhe rakatein hongi aur qaum ki teen teen . Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Yahya bin Abi Kaseer ne Abu-Salma sey, unhoney Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aisey hi riwayat kiya hai. aur aisey hi Sulaiman Yashkari ne Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha hai."
1249,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Unais ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey Khalid bin Sufiyan Hazli ke taaqqub mein Arna aur Arafat ki taraf rawana kiya aur farmaya : ''jao aur usey qatl kar do.'' maine usey dekha aur udhar namaze-Asr ka waqt ho gaya. to maine khayal kiya ke agar maine Namaz muakhkhar ki to merey aur uskey darmiyan kuch ho jaeyga . chunanche main uski taraf jatey huey isharay se Namaz padhta gaya. jab main uskey qarib hua to usney mujh se puchha : tum kon ho? maine kaha : main ehale Arab se hun aur mujhey maloom hua hai ke tum us shakhs ke muqabley ke liye lashkar jama kar rahey ho, to main is silsiley mein tumharey paas aaya hun. usney kaha : main bhi isi muhim par hun. chunanche main kuch der uskey sath chalta raha. jab maine mauqa paya to us par apni talwaar buland ki . ... yahan tak ke wo thanda ho gaya."
